# Assets Claims Amount

## identifier
de8748

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of claims that represent all on-balance sheet financial assets in all currencies in relation to all counterparty countries in accordance with accounting standards.

## guidance
Include trustee business.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.ClaimsLocal.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=instant
